{
  "stem": "20616.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only a certain number of people were permitted to enter the United States and we had to wait till the-- our number was called.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was not to be until 1937.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, to go back to the gymnasium, the school itself was a very liberal, wonderful school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- we were taught Latin, French.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had terrific teachers who were very liberal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never had any kind of problems with anti-Semitism until a new teacher came into the school, a young man by the name of Knodt.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "K-N-O-D-T.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a typical German-- version of a German Aryan-- blond, blue-eyed, tall, handsome-- and he came from [GERMAN], a special school for-- Nazi school for teachers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was assigned to this school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't think anyone had anything to say about it, whether he would be accepted or not.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was there, that's all I know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And of all things, he became my class teacher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was-- I must say, he was a very good teacher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Of course, he propagandized something terrible and there were diatribes against Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the first diatribe against Jews, he called me-- there was-- I and another, we were the only Jewish students in that class.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He called us up and he said, if I say something about Jews, I'm not talking about you personally and I'm not talking about your parents.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm just talking about Jews in general.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What were we to say about that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the diatribes continued and the students became indoctrinated, the students.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many of them had joined the [GERMAN], which is the junior-- they were too-- we were-- they were too young for the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had the younger-- the Cub Scouts, not the Boy Scouts.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
